5
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:35,840
Commander.

6
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:37,160
Come in.

7
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,360
Commander, Xue Zhihai is here.

8
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,440
How dare he come back?

9
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,680
Drive him away.

10
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:48,320
He wants to talk to you
about something important.

11
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:51,520
Let him in.

12
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:52,360
Yes.

13
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:16,080
Dongfeng, how was your chat
with Chairman Deng?

14
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:17,320
Everything goes well?

15
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:20,680
Yeah.

16
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,600
When your business grows, I'll help you.

17
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:34,160
He's still alive.

18
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,760
We meet again.

19
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,640
What brought you

20
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,680
and these men here, Zhihai?

21
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,240
I'm back to my own home.

22
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,800
Is there a problem?

23
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,280
Of course, there is.

24
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,040
No one welcomes you.

25
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,280
You almost killed Dongfeng.

26
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,840
I haven't got to you yet.

27
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,440
Now, you come to me.

28
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:01,880
Miss Qin, you've misunderstood me.

29
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:05,200
Commander Qin already
knows the whole story.

30
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,560
I don't buy it.
Who else could it be besides you?

31
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:11,320
Commander Qin will explain it to you.

32
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,320
Escort Miss Qin home.

33
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,320
I'm not leaving.

34
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,360
Please.

35
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:20,000
You're nothing but a lackey.

36
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,680
How dare you.
I'll tell my father about it.

37
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,640
It was Commander Qin who asked me

38
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,800
to send you home safely.

39
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,240
You...

40
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,400
Please, Miss Qin.

41
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,040
Xue Zhihai!

42
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,640
How bold you of you.

43
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,240
Come with me.

44
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,920
Commander Qin wants
to see you and Ji Lianyun.

45
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,640
I'll go with you.

46
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:05,680
Mr. Xue, no sight of her.

47
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,440
Governor.

48
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,520
We found Xue Zhihai
at the suburban hospital.

49
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,520
He's still alive.

50
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,680
But when I got there,

51
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,000
he was already gone.

52
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,920
He acted ahead of us.

53
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:32,920
What's wrong?

54
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:35,480
Leave here with the evidence.

55
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,200
Why now?

56
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:39,800
We'll be
in an increasingly dangerous situation

57
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,240
with the evidence in our hands.

58
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,880
A friend of mine is a reporter.

59
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,440
He will help us.

60
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:49,080
Why can't we leave together?

61
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,560
I have military duties to perform.

62
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:52,960
You leave first.

63
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,440
Is something wrong?

64
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:00,120
No, don't overthink it.

65
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,200
Make sure to keep this case safe.

66
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,040
I can't accompany you this time.

67
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,120
But I believe you can do it.

68
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,720
You must be cautious.

69
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,640
And don't show up for a while.

70
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,520
Be careful.

71
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,480
Okay, you too.

72
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:57,160
Where is Ji Lianyun?

73
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,520
Do you want to know?

74
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,320
Even if I die,

75
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,120
I won't tell you.

76
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:10,800
Dongfeng.

77
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,280
You really disappoint me.

78
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,200
I wanted you to marry my daughter

79
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:19,080
and inherit my power.

80
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,640
But what did you do?

81
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,960
You betrayed me.

82
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,760
If I want to survive in troubled times,

83
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:28,000
I have to be capable of anything.

84
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:30,400
Otherwise, how can I support so many men

85
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,640
who charge into battle for me?

86
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,960
That's not an excuse
for your wrongdoing.

87
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,880
Your crimes

88
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,560
will eventually be exposed.

89
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,080
Xue Dongfeng!

90
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,040
Don't try to challenge me.

91
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:46,360
Even if you don't tell me where she is,

92
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,120
I can still find her.

93
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,280
Guess how long
I've been waiting for this day,

94
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,720
my dear brother?

95
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:25,760
I'll make you watch yourself
lose everything.

96
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,920
So what?

97
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,480
Anyway, you never had it.

98
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,840
It's alright.

99
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:34,240
I will have it all soon.

100
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,280
You're still alive?

101
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,120
Are you expecting me to die?

102
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,920
Yes.

103
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,800
That's what I've been expecting.

104
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,840
After all, you'll see me down there.

105
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:29,040
You're heartless.

106
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,120
You hurt me first.

107
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,200
You're being petty.

108
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,040
Yes.

109
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,200
I'm so petty

110
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:48,040
that my heart belongs to only you.

111
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,760
Commander Qin has arrested Xue Dongfeng.

112
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:01,440
I've already notified Commander Qin.

113
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,080
Leave right now.

114
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,240
Zhihai.

115
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,600
Without you,

116
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,400
