117
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,600
Can you hold me?

118
00:08:41,490 --> 00:08:45,170
♪I'm waiting for the rain
to wet the city♪

119
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:48,370
♪At dusk♪

120
