124
00:09:04,130 --> 00:09:10,650
♪If your heart is as cold as ice♪

125
00:09:11,370 --> 00:09:15,690
♪My heart will call for you♪

126
00:09:15,770 --> 00:09:19,490
♪Are you as resolute as I am?♪

127
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,200
Put it down!

128
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,720
Xue Zhihai, what's the meaning of this?

129
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,000
You're also obsessed with her, right?

130
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,680
Don't be petty.

131
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:33,120
I've endured for five years.

132
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:36,160
I've been living

133
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,000
