134
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,080
because of you,

135
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,520
Xue Zhihai.

136
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,960
Starting tomorrow,

137
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,680
