140
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,880
Calm down.

141
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,640
What should I do?

142
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:58,480
I'll see you down there when I die.

143
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,720
I'll wait for you.

144
00:10:21,530 --> 00:10:25,210
♪You wake me up to see you♪

145
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:28,570
♪I'm sure your heart will be softened♪

146
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,720
That's great.

147
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:34,040
Here's to you, my dear Governor.

148
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,000
I knew

149
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:40,800
